### user registration

POST http://localhost:8080/user-api/user
Content-Type: application/json 

{
    "name":"test",
    "email":"test@gmail.com",
    "password":"test",
    "todos":[]
}

###User login
POST http://localhost:8080/user-api/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@gmail.com",
    "password": "test"
}


