###setTaskCompleted
PUT http://localhost:8080/user-api/complete-task/69315ad5ac8fc1e4bd04fdeb/69315c881b3ff70c7be207da
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "taskName":"sleeping again",
    "description":"I sleep early on this day",
    "status":"completed"   
}


